{"tid":2508581,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"數學書的正確使用方法","createTime":"2021-04-29T01:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T01:02:26.000Z","uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb5855e6349a4d66be71fff1f7dad4db511a457","tid":2508581,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"同一個概念有幾款演繹方式<br />\n有時啲野呢本書有個本書冇<br />\n揭開本書中間開始睇 發覺係睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇唔慣佢個種演繹方式 跟唔上啲步驟<br />\n會唔會每開一本新書都重頭至尾睇一次好啲<br />\n但咁樣又好似好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲書比較齊content嘅但係又proof is left as an exercise<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}